OL,3,CCrackdown on international students
OL,4,C'misusing' asylum claims to stay in UK
OL,6,FNearly 10,000 people have already been
OL,7,Fcontacted over the last week, with
OL,8,Ftens of thousands more expected to
OL,9,Freceive the guidance in the coming
OL,10,Fweeks ahead of their visas expiring.
OL,12,FThe message also warns that an asylum
OL,13,Fclaim that lacks merit will be
OL,14,F"swiftly and robustly refused".
OL,16,FThe crackdown on students is part of
OL,17,Fwider government plans to tackle
OL,18,Frising immigration, an issue which has
OL,19,Fsparked widespread protests over the
OL,20,Fsummer.
