OL,3,CCrackdown on international students
OL,4,C'misusing' asylum claims to stay in UK
OL,6,FOn Monday, the Home Secretary
OL,7,Ftemporarily suspended refugees'
OL,8,Fapplications to bring family members
OL,9,Fto the UK under the asylum system.
OL,11,FHowever, Ms Cooper said the government
OL,12,Fdoes "support refugees who have fled
OL,13,Fpersecution".
OL,15,FShe continued: "That's why we are
OL,16,Fbringing students from Gaza to be able
OL,17,Fto take up places here, but we don't
OL,18,Fwant to see the asylum system misused
OL,19,Fby students who simply want to stay
OL,20,Ffor longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
