OL,3,CCrackdown on international students
OL,4,C'misusing' asylum claims to stay in UK
OL,6,FConservative MP Andrew Bowie said the
OL,7,Fgovernment's wider plans do not go far
OL,8,Fenough: "As of yet, there's no
OL,9,Fdeterrent factor.
OL,11,F"They got rid of Rwanda, which was the
OL,12,Fone deterrent factor we had, without
OL,13,Fone plane taking off. I think that was
OL,14,Fa huge mistake."
OL,16,FHe added, "We all hope that these
OL,17,Factions will work. We just don't know
OL,18,Fif they will."
